    "en": {
      "title": "A young man was killed in a shooting in Mattakuliya",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that a person has been killed in a shooting that took place in Mattakkuli last night. The murder was caused by a pistol shot by two persons on a motorcycle.",
        "The 26-year-old victim died while being admitted to the Colombo National Hospital. The police suspect that organized crime related to drugs is the reason for this murder."
      ],
